dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Paul Powell. May I have your name, please?
Hello Paul, my name is Kathryn Phillips.
Nice to meet you, Kathryn. Can you please provide me with your policy number and date of birth for verification purposes?
Sure, my policy number is eight seven two four five and my date of birth is zero five nine eight, nineteen eighty-four.
Thank you, Kathryn. One more thing, can you confirm your current address and contact number for our records?
Of course, my address is two one four Oak Street, Springfield and my contact number is five five five, two three four, one zero zero zero.
Thank you for providing the information, Kathryn. Is there anything else I can assist you with today?
No, that's all for now. Thank you for your help, Paul.
You're welcome, Kathryn. If you have any more questions in the future, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
